description: Demolition and redevelopment of existing structures for a residential-led mixed use development comprising a series of buildings, ranging up to 38 storeys in height. Provision of 860no. residential dwellings (Class C3) and Student Accommodation (Sui Generis), flexible commercial (Class E) at ground floor and a replacement food retail store (Class E). Provision of central green public space, new areas of public realm, private landscaped amenity spaces, ancillary cycle and car spaces and all necessary ancillary and enabling works. This application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement. A cover letter detailing the amendments is available on the online record.
